<h1>User#show</h1>
<%= render :partial => "profile_menu" %>


<p>Ime: <%= @user.first_name %></p>
<p>Prezime: <%= @user.last_name %></p>
<p>Email: <%= @user.email %></p>
<p>Telefon: <%= @user.phone %></p>
<p>Prebivaliste: <%= @user.residence %></p>
<p>Mjesto rodjenja: <%= @user.birthplace %></p>
<p>Datum rodjenja: <%= @user.birthdate %></p>
<p>Aktivan? <%= @user.is_active %></p>
<p>Diplomirao? <%= @user.graduated %></p>
<p>Smjer: <%= @user.department %></p>
<p>Broj indeksa: <%= @user.index_nmb %></p>
<p>Godina upisa studija: <%= @user.enrolment_year %></p>
<p>Datum pristupa BIUSu: <%= @user.join_date %></p>

<hr/>

Clan sekcija:
<ul>
<% for section in @user.sections %>
<li><%= link_to section.title, :controller=>'sections', :action=>'show', :id=>section.id %></li>
<% end %>
</ul>

Sudionik projekata:
<ul>
<% for project in @user.projects %>
<li><%= link_to project.title, :controller=>'projects', :action=>'show', :id=>project.id %></li>
<% end %>
</ul>

Predmeti trenutno kod clana:
<ul>
<% for itemhist in @user.items_in_possession %>
<li> 
<%= link_to "#{itemhist.item.inv_no} | #{itemhist.item.name}" , :controller => 'items' , :action => 'show' , :id => itemhist.item.id %> |
<%= link_to 'Oslobodi predmet' , :controller=>'items' , :action => 'dealloc' , :id => itemhist.item.id , :requester_id => session[:user_id] %>
</li>

<% end %>
</ul>

Predmeti u proslosti kod clana:
<ul>
<% for itemhist in @user.items_taken %>
<li> <%= link_to "#{itemhist.item.inv_no} | #{itemhist.item.name}" , :controller => 'items' , :action => 'show' , :id => itemhist.item.id %> </li>
<% end %>
</ul>
